  <!-- EN: flare gun -->
  <CE_FlareGun.label>信号枪</CE_FlareGun.label>
  <!-- EN: An ancient, single-shot flare gun, used for signaling or illumination. Loaded from the breech, its barrel is too thin to fire anything but flares. -->
  <CE_FlareGun.description>一种古老的单发信号枪，用于发信号或照明。弹药从信号枪的后膛装载。由于信号枪枪管太薄，所以只能发射信号弹。</CE_FlareGun.description>
