  <!-- EN: minigun -->
  <CE_MechanoidMinigun.label>机械族速射机枪</CE_MechanoidMinigun.label>
  <!-- EN: A multi-barrel machine gun. It looks menacing with its long barrels and once it starts firing it fires very fast. Where most self-loading guns are powered by the energy from the gunpowder, the minigun uses an electric motor powered by the mechanoid it's mounted on to rapidly cycle cartridges through the weapon. -->
  <CE_MechanoidMinigun.description>古老的多管机枪，拥有极高的射速。虽然笨重但火力强大。在大多数自动武器使用火药提供动力的情况下，这种武器使用一种电动机使子弹能够快速替换。</CE_MechanoidMinigun.description>
  <!-- EN: barrel -->
  <CE_MechanoidMinigun.tools.barrel.label>枪管</CE_MechanoidMinigun.tools.barrel.label>
  <!-- EN: minigun -->
  <CE_MechanoidMinigun.verbs.Verb_ShootCE.label>机械族速射机枪</CE_MechanoidMinigun.verbs.Verb_ShootCE.label>
  
  <!-- EN: thermal bolt projector -->
  <CE_ThermalBoltProjector.label>热能弹发射器</CE_ThermalBoltProjector.label>
  <!-- EN: A medium-velocity, low-trajectory fire support system deployed by mechanoids. While inaccurate and slow-firing, it remains a potent weapon against static targets. -->
  <CE_ThermalBoltProjector.description>一种机械族使用的中速低弹道武器，虽然精准度不高而且射速慢，但仍然能高效的对付躲在掩体后的静止目标。</CE_ThermalBoltProjector.description>
  <!-- EN: barrel -->
  <CE_ThermalBoltProjector.tools.barrel.label>枪管</CE_ThermalBoltProjector.tools.barrel.label>
